<br>
<p>WOW. I cannot disagree more.  I think the setting is the heart and soul of ED. Without it, its just another in a long line of generic fantasy systems.  I'll agree some of the adventures were lacking, but other then that I greatly enjoy almost all of the metaplot and setting.</p>
</font></td>
